text: COVID literally stands for Chinese Originated Viral Infectious Disease.
COVID-19 is named so because it is the 19th Chinese-Originated Viral Infectious Disease.
An image shared on Facebook claims the acronym COVID in COVID-19 stands for Chinese Originated Viral Infectious Disease and the number 19 represents it being the 19th virus to come out of China.
COVID is an acronym that stands for discovered (and yet to be discovered) variants of COVID-19.
An image shared on Facebook claims the acronym COVID in COVID-19 stands for Certificate Of Vaccination Identification.
COVID-19 stands for Certificate of Vaccination ID, with the number 19 representing the letters AI, for Artificial Intelligence.
